freenet.node
Class RequestStarter

java.lang.Object
  freenet.node.RequestStarter
All Implemented Interfaces:
RandomGrabArrayItemExclusionList, Runnable
public class RequestStarter
extends Object
implements Runnable, RandomGrabArrayItemExclusionList

Starts requests. Nobody starts a request directly, you have to go through RequestStarter. And you have to provide a RequestStarterClient. We do round robin between clients on the same priority level.
